author: Al Jazeera
title: White House projects 100,000-240,000 US deaths from coronavirus
description: Trump calls efforts to slow the spread of the virus 'a matter of life and death' and warns of a 'rough' two weeks ahead.
content:
The White House on Tuesday projected 100,000 to 240,000 deaths in the United State from the coronavirus pandemic even if current social distancing guidelines are maintained.
